#### Algorithm

1. Calculate the KNN Distances using the distance matrix
2. Calculate the Volume of the unit ball wrt d_dimensions
3. Calculate the entropy measure

$$H = \log (N - 1) - \psi(k) + \log (v) + D * \frac{1}{N} \sum \log D$$
